device : cookie : session
-------:--------:--------
111111 :        : 123
222222 :        : 


- process starts at first entry in MSG_QUEUE...
- check for cookie in SESSION table using deviceId as key
- if no, continue to next entry in MSG_QUEUE...
- else yes,
    - if startSession,
       - call startSession
       - upon callback
          - append gameSessionId to SESSION table using deviceId as key
          - remove startSession from MSG_QUEUE
       - continue to next entry in MSG_QUEUE...
    - else telem,
       - check for session in SESSION table using deviceId as key
       - if no, continue to next entry in MSG_QUEUE...
       - else yes,
          - call sendTelemetry
          - upon callback
             - remove sendTelemetry from MSG_QUEUE
          - continue to next entry in MSG_QUEUE...
    - else endSession,
       - call endSession
       - upon callback
          - remove gameSessionId from SESSION table using deviceId as key
          - remove endSession from MSG_QUEUE
       - continue to next entry in MSG_QUEUE


no cookie
no internet
msg queue only executes if you have internet and cookie
only send your device Id information
must begin with startsession when switching between users


